abcde Flash

Schweiz, 2022, 6 Min, english

The menstrual cycle has four phases, and abcde Flash has mastered them all. From the oh-so-draining ovulation (a period of rest), to the absolute mind-fuckery of the luteal phase (social interactions can wait), she arrives at the follicular and menstruation phases, where creativity easily flows (and anything goes!).
title: Grace.
